o From the 18 month anniversary of the chapter 11 

petition date through December 31, 2013: $2.0 billion 
(plus accrued interest); and 

o From January 1, 2014 until mandatory conversion: $2.1 

billion (plus accrued interest). 

? Annual interest to commence accrual as of the chapter 11 petition 

date: 4% PIK through December 31, 2013; 8% PIK from January 1, 
2014 through December 31, 2014; and 12% at all times thereafter. 
